    "Materials and methods Case collectionWe conducted a retrospective review of the files of glaucomatous patients who underwent any type of surgical or Key messages What is known:Artificial Intelligence-powered chatbots, such as ChatGPT and Google Gemini, have been heralded as revolutionary turning points in the current AI revolution and tested in other medicine subspecialties, such as neurology, neurosurgery or emergency.",
    "What is new:ChatGPT showed promising results in the analysis of glaucoma clinical cases, being able to produce a coherent surgical plan in the majority of cases.Google Gemini showed high rates of unprecise and missed answers, along with less detailed and more synthetic analysis of clinical scenarios.In complicated scenarios, the difficulty in computing heterogeneous conditions emerge, but ChatGPT was able to provide accurate and complete answers, demonstrating multimodal reasoning skills and significantly outperforming Google Gemini.para-surgical glaucoma treatment in Policlinico Universitario Agostino Gemelli between May 2019 and October 2023.",
    "This study adhered to the tenets of the Declaration of Helsinki, and the Institutional review board (IRB) approval was obtained from the Policlinico Universitario Agostino Gemelli Institutional Ethics Committee.We selected a total of 66 medical records from a pool of over 250.",
    "Patient demographics and medical or ocular anamnesis, actual ocular diseases and topical medication, referred symptoms, and examination results were all described in detail in each instance.",
